metadata.name: Unstable Civilian #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the official NFT collection of mental health , every second of the day all over the world we all struggle at some point . Our goal is to touch as many hearts as possible  to re assure people they aren't alone , and we are all in this together and for each other . Our team put together a collection of 3K NFTS with daily aspirations to help get them through tough times , this is more than NFTs - This  is a movement for the silent majority it's time to make noise

attributes.value: I'll be okay with or without
